0-07-18T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"睇第二間 拎多啲資訊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"佢已經好返 仲有得搵second opinion?"},{"pid":"732765077935f9dd6c3609ac2ff22b6591a5c97e","tid":2114131,"uid":83418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"702cb0fe0fcdabda38645d97f4632f1841575177","tid":2114131,"uid":148392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68fcc144393e15d2c92951e5d279766871e7e819","tid":2114131,"uid":224270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"睇第二間 拎多啲資訊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"佢已經好返 仲有得搵second opinion?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T15:01:58.000Z","msg":"睇第二間可能會睇到你本身去果間睇唔到嘅問題，唔嫌遠可以試下北角npv，價錢比其他診所本，醫生姑娘都有禮貌，前提係你都有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdde25a193c7c4dea9d018310ceb4cf8ff8b0eea","tid":2114131,"uid":83418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T15:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇第二間 拎多啲資訊</blockquote>佢已經好返 仲有得搵second opinion?</blockquote>睇第二間可能會睇到你本身去果間睇唔到嘅問題，唔嫌遠可以試下北角npv，價錢比其他診所<span class=\"red\">平</span>，醫生姑娘都有禮貌，前提係你都有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"01bed0307749db4d70894c16e3590ad57a2a6c36","tid":2114131,"uid":332327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a7f1261532995345deba996aa0ea251bebb9b2d5","tid":2114131,"uid":148392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:42:11.000Z","msg":"醫生最後話係敗血症(sepsis) 事隔差唔多一個月 經過4日住院2次覆診食咗半個月藥 我隻貓仔終於好返哂啦(除咗把聲變咗老牛聲)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日打咗去絕育個間診所叫佢比返個交代我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢地就推得一乾二淨<br />\n話佢地手術完全無問題 好大機會係肺炎(住院份report完全無提過) 一離就好有可能因為係我地餵水入錯咗格<br />\n<br />\n但係發現貓仔病既第一同第二日朝早（分別係絕育個間同入院間診所）都照過chest X-ray <br />\n話個肺係好清完全無問題無發炎<br />\n係到咗第二日既晏晝 醫生聽到貓仔個肺有雜音照多咗張chest X-ray 個陣就見到個左肺middle lobe白咗 佢就解釋係因為佢抖氣用太大力太辛苦所以出現肺硬化既情況<br />\n到第三日貓仔先出現咳同埋有痰既徵狀 <br />\n<br />\n我就同絕育診所個護士講哂宜堆野同埋不斷強調個diagnosis係sepsis而唔係肺炎<br />\n佢竟然答可能係因為肺炎係初期 所以X-ray先睇唔到同埋貓貓仔係咳無痰 話一定唔關手術事 仲話double confirm咗醫生話份report無寫係敗血症(我就咁睇都已經寫咗最少兩次 佢竟然好肯定話無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n話手術係開肚同埋傷口都係肚 sepsis既話一定會有腹膜炎而唔係肺炎<br />\n<br />\n之後我就再答report寫貓仔係敗血病而唔係肺炎 我話不如圈完send比你 你問清楚醫生再同我講啦 <br />\n<br />\n想搵各位清可以解答下以下既問題？<br />\n1) sepsis既原因可唔可以係經針頭注射入血？唔一定係經傷口入？<br />\n2) 貓既病毒性肺炎同細菌性肺炎係咪同人一樣 細菌性肺炎既病徵係會好明顯？ 唔會一d病徵都無？<br />\n3)有冇可能真係係佢所講咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後續個護士仲要勁臭串<br />\n1) 我地講咗成20分鐘都係想佢認係因為手術搞到我隻貓咁 起碼都負責任同我講返聲sorry啊 (我都想佢負責返部分既醫藥費既但係個機會太渺茫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲係學生好窮）<br />\n然後佢都一直唔認答唔到就唔清楚 答到就串過馬撚 佢其中一句係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lsquo;你兜圈其實好耐啊 成件事都係講返個一點 不如你直接同我講你地既目的係想我地做d咩野或者我地做咩補償&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n2）勁唔耐煩 係咁重覆話 &lsquo;我同你講咗好多次&rsquo;<br />\n3）因為佢要再睇多次份report 我話你睇完 我再打返過離同你討論啦 佢就話可能會唔通 之後就收線 連88都唔講<br />\n<br />\n附上貓貓j圖3張 （唐貓lives matter!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vsXvf3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7vsXvf3.png&h=b2ecc7e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6JM1WV7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6JM1WV7.png&h=6e459922&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fkQaQgd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfkQaQgd.png&h=b9f7ed65&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"可唔可以分享係邊間診所 避免貓奴或主人幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99775ab8c10d30be499c484af997f026eabd01e6","tid":2114131,"uid":148392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"732765077935f9dd6c3609ac2ff22b6591a5c97e","tid":2114131,"uid":83418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"702cb0fe0fcdabda38645d97f4632f1841575177","tid":2114131,"uid":148392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68fcc144393e15d2c92951e5d279766871e7e819","tid":2114131,"uid":224270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"睇第二間 拎多啲資訊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"佢已經好返 仲有得搵second opinion?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T15:01:58.000Z","msg":"睇第二間可能會睇到你本身去果間睇唔到嘅問題，唔嫌遠可以試下北角npv，價錢比其他診所本，醫生姑娘都有禮貌，前提係你都有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T15:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jHpCvtQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjHpCvtQ.gif&h=217c48a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b71cca78f7c1b86ae2d4922ec918af8aa12053f8","tid":2114131,"uid":263538,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27358910aa05124075f0bc4f1823afc71831aa8c","tid":2114131,"uid":7824,"like":2,"dislike":56,"score":-54,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:43:09.000Z","msg":"買過第二隻啦 呢啲唐貓好平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T15:59:47.000Z","msg":"真係忍唔住屌你同你老母"}]}